title: CUFF IT | Choreography by Master Ram #RawStudios #MasterRam #Ram #Beyoncé #cuffit
description:
RAW Studios is a platform providing professional and inspiring body-and-mind activities that engage each individual to lead an active and healthy life with a vast array of activities:  Dance, Fitness, Yoga, Photography and more.  

RAW Studios is founded by Master Ram:

A leading choreographer and instructor in Asia including India, Singapore, Thailand, China and HK; teaching thousands of students and more than 20 genres in the past 2 decades
A trainer of dance teachers and performers
A certified yoga instructor for multi levels and genres 
A fitness instructor helping students achieve their health goals
A creative videographer and photographer

Raw Studios is currently based in India and Hong Kong, but its coverage is universal.  It strives to pursue multiple-facet projects with the goal to share its visions, hoping to inspire others to feel fulfilled and confident.
